{"tid":477643,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[偉大] 蘋果留在中國是為了推動言論自由權益","createTime":"2017-11-23T08:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T08:53:55.000Z","uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47634f2de6d76e33d88d113b26ed0da54fa7f5e8","tid":477643,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">674 VPN應用程式下架 狡辯：要留喺中國推言論自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171123/large/1511408804_2816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171123%2Flarge%2F1511408804_2816.jpg&h=a5392d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國蘋果公司於當地時間21日承認，應中國政府要求，今年已下架中國區應用商店（App Store）內的674個VPN應用程式。蘋果解釋，這樣做使公司得以繼續留在中國，從而推動言論自由等基本權益。<br />\n<br />\n今年10月，美國參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）和萊希（Patrick Leahy）聯名致函蘋果公司行政總裁庫克，質疑蘋果公司下架VPN的決定。蘋果公司作出相關回應。該兩名美國參議員說，防火長城對中國人民的威脅，不亞於28年前柏林圍牆對東德人民的威脅。只要防火長城在，並獲得美國技術公司的支持，中國的互聯網自由就仍處於風險中。<br />\n蘋果公司在回信中提到，該公司在中國的存在「有助於促進更大程度的開放，推動思想和信息的自由流動」。蘋果公司公共政策副總裁Cynthia Hogan辯稱：「我們深信，讓蘋果公司能最好地推動基本權益， 包括言論自由權的方式就是參與，儘管我們可能不同意某些國家的法律。」蘋果公司表示，曾質詢過中國當局要求下架VPN的法律依據。當局回覆，這些軟件違反中國法律，包括《網絡安全法》第27條等。<br />\n<br />\nVPN稱為虛擬私人網絡，可以改變並加密用戶的互聯網接入地址。在防火長城高聳的中國，網民們用此來繞開互聯網封鎖，即所謂的「翻牆」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171123/57493564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171123%2F57493564&d=vvZaVjXVMljUr7jM103PqJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4e89d5aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171123%2F57493564&h=161b7714\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171123/57493564</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAPPLE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5687134e92893152db0880ef019afc97a710d052","tid":477643,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"唔妥協又點堅持呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62ac26e346023d1585c4a152d5b5b42f03c85e7","tid":477643,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"忍辱負重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adfd141d03aa37a07e549717fc0290ab58d65fd","tid":477643,"uid":41849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"APPLE GD JOB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好再放班狗出黎咬人"},{"pid":"336bfaa2ca256cf5430b2468e44942a7e7f2d9cb","tid":477643,"uid":123597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:50:51.000Z","msg":"香港行互聯網，大陸行內聯網"},{"pid":"fa44abef103044d6de63222836bfcd8850fba51b","tid":477643,"uid":15235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 少左好多大陸狗係到亂吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}